\v 1 \x - \xo 4:1 \xt Wok Me 10:42, Rom 14:9-10\x*Timoti, t…ôkwt…ôkwuni iakam…ô…°kiari pehe mik r…ômwhen krau krou…ôrer ia n…ômri Kumwes…ôn m…®ne Iesu Kristo. Ikukur…ôn Iesu Kristo in i…ôrmama s…ô tr…ôkiri n…ôrmama me pam t…® noien me s…ôv…ônraha, n…ôrmama s…ôm…ôme kamh…ôm…®ru m…®ne s…ôm…ôme h…ôuvamh…ô raka. In trier pehe mwi m…ôr…®m…ônu ia n…®t…ôt…ô s…ôv…ônhi. T…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô tro iam…®nhi ir…ô, ro pen iakani pehe tukw ik i m…ô
\v 2 \x - \xo 4:2 \xt Wok Me 20:20,31\x*tikam…ôkeikei m…ôvisau irapw n…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ônhi, mam…ôrer mwatuk tukwe ia n…ôp…®n me pam, n…ôp…®n n…ôrmama hokeikei m…ô tuh…ôre…°i m…®ne n…ôp…®n n…ôrmama h…ôpw…ôh nokeikeiien m…ô tuh…ôre…°i. Tik…®ni pui noien …ôr…ôha me s…ôv…ônraha, m…®nise pen …ôknek…®n t…® nir…ôha m…ô tuh…ôpw…ôh, muvei pen n…ô…°kiariien s…ô trasitu ia nir…ôha, mo iam…®nhi ir…ô s…ôim n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien r…ôpw…ômw…®s, n…ôn…ô, mahat…ôn amasan ir…ôha.
